</div>]]></content:encoded></item><item><title>【實試】TCL 8K Mini LED 電視開箱，極強色彩、解像度表現 + ONKYO 震撼低音喇叭</title><link>https://unwire.hk/2022/06/16/tcl-8k-mini-led/wireless-home/audio-visual/?utm_source=rss&amp;utm_medium=rss&amp;utm_campaign=tcl-8k-mini-led</link><dc:creator><![CDATA[Lawton]]></dc:creator><pubDate>Thu, 16 Jun 2022 12:15:25 +0000</pubDate><category><![CDATA[影音產品]]></category><category><![CDATA[8K]]></category><category><![CDATA[mini-LED]]></category><category><![CDATA[TCL]]></category><guid isPermaLink="false">https://unwire.hk/?p=1104709</guid><description><![CDATA[<p>Mini LED 電視產品已在市場上逐漸推出，而 TCL 就推出了全新旗艦機 X925 8K Mini LED [&#8230;]</p></p>]]></description><content:encoded><![CDATA[<p>Mini LED 電視產品已在市場上逐漸推出，而 TCL 就推出了全新旗艦機 X925 8K Mini LED，並以 75 吋大尺寸登場。它用上 Mini LED 極細光源組，配合 8K 處理器提供極強的圖像解像度與光表現的對比度。這部旗艦級電視更內置了 ONKYO 2.1 聲道音響系統，在平薄電視上裝設有大型低音喇叭，收看電影時震撼力更是不同凡響。</p><p><a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/06/unwire0059.jpg"><img loading="lazy" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1104732" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/06/unwire0059-694x468.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="468" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/06/unwire0059-694x468.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/06/unwire0059-768x518.jpg 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/06/unwire0059.jpg 1039w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></a></p><p><a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/06/unwire0037.jpg"><img loading="lazy" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1104730" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/06/unwire0037-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/06/unwire0037-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/06/unwire0037-768x432.jpg 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/06/unwire0037.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></a></p><p>今次小編得到 TCL 協助下，實際開箱了一部全新的旗艦機 TCL X925 8K Mini LED 電視。75 吋電視的大小確是頗為震撼，如果放一部任天堂 Switch 去旁邊，看上去都變成了一部舊 iPhone 5。不過此機採用了超薄金屬邊框設計，比起想像中不佔空間，迅速與家居融合。</p><p><a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/06/IMG_4567-scaled.jpg"><img loading="lazy" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1104712" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/06/IMG_4567-694x419.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="419" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/06/IMG_4567-694x419.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/06/IMG_4567-1280x773.jpg 1280w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/06/IMG_4567-768x464.jpg 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/06/IMG_4567-1536x927.jpg 1536w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/06/IMG_4567-2048x1237.jpg 2048w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/06/IMG_4567-scaled.jpg 1600w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></a><a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/06/unwire0098.jpg"><img loading="lazy" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1104717" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/06/unwire0098-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/06/unwire0098-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/06/unwire0098-768x432.jpg 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/06/unwire0098.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></a></p><p><a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/06/unwire0095.jpg"><img loading="lazy" class="aligncenter wp-image-1104716 size-large" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/06/unwire0095-506x900.jpg" alt="" width="506" height="900" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/06/unwire0095-506x900.jpg 506w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/06/unwire0095-326x580.jpg 326w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/06/unwire0095-768x1365.jpg 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/06/unwire0095-864x1536.jpg 864w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/06/unwire0095-1152x2048.jpg 1152w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/06/unwire0095.jpg 900w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 506px" /></a></p><p><a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/06/unwire0008.jpg"><img loading="lazy" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1104733" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/06/unwire0008-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/06/unwire0008-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/06/unwire0008-768x432.jpg 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/06/unwire0008.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></a></p><h2>8K 超高解像度與 Mini LED 帶來與別不同的對比度</h2><p>8K 電視當然提供了令人感到震撼的畫質，在 YouTube 上可找到好多 8K 影片，我們可直接選擇 4320p（即 8K）畫質，實際播放時解像度為 7680*4320。播放時可享受極高解像度。TCL 這部旗艦 Mini LED 使用到 Quantum Dot 量子點技術、全陣列區域調光技術，電視收看夜景影像時，更加突顯到 Mini LED 的特性，與高達 1,000 nits 光亮度的屏幕，陰暗部與光亮度的光度差特別大，所能感受到的畫面細緻度比一般電視更加好。例如夜景中的燈光會比一般電視更為光亮，而一個範圍發光，在高對比度下，不會造成強烈光暈，令附近範圍所顯示的黑色更為紥實。</p><p><a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/06/unwire0065.jpg"><img loading="lazy" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1104721" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/06/unwire0065-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/06/unwire0065-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/06/unwire0065-768x432.jpg 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/06/unwire0065.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></a></p><p><a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/06/unwire0066.jpg"><img loading="lazy" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1104722" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/06/unwire0066-694x486.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="486" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/06/unwire0066-694x486.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/06/unwire0066-768x537.jpg 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/06/unwire0066.jpg 969w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></a><a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/06/unwire0060.jpg"><img loading="lazy" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1104723" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/06/unwire0060-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/06/unwire0060-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/06/unwire0060-768x432.jpg 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/06/unwire0060.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></a></p><p><a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/06/unwire0057.jpg"><img loading="lazy" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1104724" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/06/unwire0057-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/06/unwire0057-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/06/unwire0057-768x432.jpg 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/06/unwire0057.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></a></p><p>本機熒幕支援 HDR 10+ 與 Dolby Vision IQ，支援大部份影片與最常用的串流影片服務如 Netflix、Disney+ 等。電視支援 Dolby Vision IQ，現時好多電影、Netflix 劇集都支援這項技術，播放時可令畫面有更好的動態範圍，顯示更光亮的亮部，以及細緻演繹的暗部位置。</p><p><a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/06/unwire0081.jpg"><img loading="lazy" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1104725" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/06/unwire0081-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/06/unwire0081-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/06/unwire0081-768x432.jpg 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/06/unwire0081.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></a> <a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/06/unwire0085.jpg"><img loading="lazy" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1104726" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/06/unwire0085-694x479.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="479" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/06/unwire0085-694x479.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/06/unwire0085-768x530.jpg 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/06/unwire0085.jpg 999w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></a></p><p>在測試 Disney+ 影片時，就用得著本機支援的 IMAX ENHANCED 功能。相比起一般電影會留上下黑邊，IMAX ENHANCED 可把畫面內容尺寸加大，以令上下黑邊都能顯示內容。播放支援的影片，如《尚氣》，畫面黑邊消失再加上 75 吋大熒幕，所帶來的震撼力更大。</p><p><a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/06/unwire0055.jpg"><img loading="lazy" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1104731" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/06/unwire0055-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/06/unwire0055-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/06/unwire0055-768x432.jpg 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/06/unwire0055.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></a></p><p><a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/06/unwire0000.jpg"><img loading="lazy" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1104728" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/06/unwire0000-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/06/unwire0000-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/06/unwire0000-768x432.jpg 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/06/unwire0000.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></a></p><p><a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/06/unwire0005.jpg"><img loading="lazy" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1104727" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/06/unwire0005-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/06/unwire0005-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/06/unwire0005-768x432.jpg 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/06/unwire0005.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></a></p><p>在電視的設定畫面中，有動態亮度、區域背光、區域對比度等選項，全部開啟這些選項可讓你有更亮麗的畫面。</p><p><a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/06/unwire0028-1.jpg"><img loading="lazy" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1104729" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/06/unwire0028-1-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/06/unwire0028-1-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/06/unwire0028-1-768x432.jpg 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/06/unwire0028-1.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></a></p><p>TCL X925 8K Mini LED 旗艦級電視還支援 MEMC 120Hz 技術，能夠把一般影像升頻至 120Hz，影片播放時展現更佳的流暢感覺。而電視當然也支援 120Hz 的次世代遊戲機如 PS5, Xbox Series X 等。</p><h2>超薄電視內置 ONKYO 2.1 喇叭、重低音喇叭 30W 輸出</h2><p>電視機身已內置了 ONKYO 2.1 聲道音響組合，當中 2 個每個輸出功率 15W 的向上喇叭，在後面我們更看到一個輸出功率達到 30W 的低音喇叭。就算不裝設任何 Soundbar，這套支援 Dolby Atmos 的 2.1 聲道喇叭都有不錯的臨場感，特別震撼的重低音音效。</p><p><a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/06/unwire0100.jpg"><img loading="lazy" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1104718" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/06/unwire0100-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/06/unwire0100-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/06/unwire0100-768x432.jpg 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/06/unwire0100.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></a></p><p><a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/06/unwire0089.jpg"><img loading="lazy" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1104715" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/06/unwire0089-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/06/unwire0089-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/06/unwire0089-768x432.jpg 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/06/unwire0089.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></a><a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/06/unwire0091.jpg"><img loading="lazy" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1104719" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/06/unwire0091-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/06/unwire0091-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/06/unwire0091-768x432.jpg 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/06/unwire0091.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></a></p><p>電視已內置 Wi-Fi 6 連接與 LAN 連接，我們測試無線 Wi-Fi 連接播放 8K 影片，連接速度超過 150Mbps，都能長期保持畫面暢順。</p><p>電視本身已支援 Android TV 平臺，電視已內置 Netflix、Disney+、YouTube、Amazon Prime Video、Apple TV 等常用串流 App，用戶亦可自行到 Google Play（Android TV 版本）下載不同種類的應用程式，如 ViuTV 等。電視附有 2 個遙控，一個是紅外線傳輸另一個是藍牙連接，雙方都有 Netflix、Prime Video、YouTube 以及內置媒體播放器的一鍵按鈕，遙控也支援語音輸入，在 Google、YouTube 搜尋影片時更加方便。</p><p><a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/06/unwire0034-2.jpg"><img loading="lazy" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1104720" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/06/unwire0034-2-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/06/unwire0034-2-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/06/unwire0034-2-768x432.jpg 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/06/unwire0034-2.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></a></p><p><a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/06/unwire0031.jpg"><img loading="lazy" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1104714" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/06/unwire0031-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/06/unwire0031-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/06/unwire0031-768x432.jpg 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/06/unwire0031.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></a></p><h2>總結：震撼影視效果，擁有出色色彩演繹</h2><p>TCL X925 覆蓋 100% 以上 DCI-P3 色域，再加上 Mini LED 與 8K 解像度的細緻表示，在收看 8K 內容時帶來了極為清晰細緻的影像體驗。超薄電視裡面裝設大型 30W 重低音揚聲器，配合 Netflix、Disney+ 支援到 IMAX ENHANCED、Dolby Atmos 的影片，令視覺、音覺體驗進一步提升。處理器在運行各種應用程式、播放器播片都極為暢順，沒有特別要等候的感覺，電視附隨 2 個遙控就更加貼心。今時今日大家都追求家居影視全新享受，可考慮這類使用 Mini LED 等新技術的大型電視。</p><p><a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/06/unwire0067.jpg"><img loading="lazy" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1104734" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/06/unwire0067-694x521.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="521" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/06/unwire0067-694x521.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/06/unwire0067-768x577.jpg 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/06/unwire0067.jpg 888w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></a></p><p>至於打機方面，今次實試的 X925 已支援 120Hz 更新率，而想打機流暢度、遊戲影像演繹更好，可留意支援 144Hz VRR（動態更新率）的 TCL Mini LED 4K 電視。</p><p>TCL X925 8K Mini LED TV</p><p>尺寸：75 吋</p><p>官方建議零售價：$79,800</p><p><a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/06/unwire0105.jpg"><img loading="lazy" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1104735" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/06/unwire0105-694x390.j